name: TokenSetsInteractiveAdapter
description: Interactive adapter for TokenSets. Implementation of InteractiveAdapter abstract contract.

functionDecorators.name: deposit
functionDecorators.description: Deposits tokens to the TokenSet. Implementation of InteractiveAdapter function.

parameterDecorators.name: tokens
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - payment token address.

parameterDecorators.name: amounts
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - payment token amount to be deposited.

parameterDecorators.name: amountTypes
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - amount type.

parameterDecorators.name: data
parameterDecorators.description: ABI-encoded additional parameters: - rebalancingSetAddress - rebalancing set address; - rebalancingSetQuantity - rebalancing set amount to be minted;.

returnDecorators.description: Asset sent back to the msg.sender.
Amount of SetTokens held by the given account.

functionDecorators.name: withdraw
functionDecorators.description: Withdraws tokens from the TokenSet. Implementation of InteractiveAdapter function.

parameterDecorators.name: tokens
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - rebalancing set address.

parameterDecorators.name: amounts
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - rebalancing set amount to be burned.

parameterDecorators.name: amountTypes
parameterDecorators.description: Array with one element - amount type.

returnDecorators.description: Asset sent back to the msg.sender.
